{"tid":973619,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"貶損奏唱國歌囚3年 行會通過國歌法草案本月交立會審議","createTime":"2019-01-08T09:57:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-09T15:51:11.000Z","uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1de2e02da31f60562d67613bdef0eca2776a8426","tid":973619,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T09:57:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190108/large/1546925338_4733.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190108%2Flarge%2F1546925338_4733.png&h=a3cefd42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n醞釀多時的《國歌法》本地立法草案正式出台！據了解，政制及內地事務局已完成《國歌條例草案》草擬工作，行會成員向《蘋果》證實，行會今日正式通過有關建議，料本月內提交至立法會進行首讀。據當局早前向議員「摸底」的建議，除了國慶、回歸等重要節日，涉及行政，司法及立法的宣誓儀式均是播國歌的場合。法案中亦設有兩項罰則，列明任何人公開、故意篡改國歌，或以歪曲、貶損方式奏唱國歌，最高可判監3年、罰款5萬元。政制及內地事務局局長聶德權將於明日(9日)開記招解釋條例草案，該局副秘書長李佩詩和首席助理秘書長林瑋琦亦會出席。<br />\n<br />\n全國人大常委會前年年底通過《國歌法》，並將《國歌法》納入香港《基本法》附件三，由特區政府負責本地立法落實。政制及內地事務局去年底已大致完成草擬工作，並向各大黨派的議員作出遊說，除了要求列明任何人公開及故意篡改國歌歌詞、曲譜，以歪曲、貶損方式奏唱國歌，即屬犯法，亦規定中小學需要教授國歌。當局最近又提出新元素，指特首、行會成員、法官及立法會議員的宣誓儀式前亦須播放國歌。<br />\n<br />\n部份民主派議員曾表明反對《國歌法》，議會陣線指會考慮在法案委員會提出修正案，加入條文要求刪除有關立法會議員就職宣誓時要播國歌的要求。議員朱凱廸曾指，今次立法源於香港有球迷在球場噓國歌，批評「根本呢場大龍鳳係大到離晒譜」，目的為迫香港主動表達愛國情操。據知，民主派即使未見統一立場，但都會動員加入法案委員會，在委員會就立法細節向政府提出質詢。<br />\n<br />\n公民黨黨魁楊岳橋指，《國歌法》中仍未曾就貶損國歌有清晰的定義表示憂慮，亦對於立法會宣誓儀式前須播放國歌的安排表示質疑，擔心成為政府DQ異見議員的其中一個新增藉口，他指國歌法侵害言論和表達自由，故公民黨會反對國歌法立法。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190108/large/1546937159_e964.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190108%2Flarge%2F1546937159_e964.png&h=c9b14ec1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190108/large/1546937159_4120.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190108%2Flarge%2F1546937159_4120.png&h=baf05327&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190108/large/1546937158_d515.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190108%2Flarge%2F1546937158_d515.png&h=675ec55d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190108/large/1546937824_09be.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190108%2Flarge%2F1546937824_09be.png&h=22f90154&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190108/59117924?fbclid=IwAR1O8vKbaOmP0Tz_96Cm6NjyU2LaJ46W7nBnl_Z3I-4a5gLBiXvN6klPdvY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190108%2F59117924%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1O8vKbaOmP0Tz_96Cm6NjyU2LaJ46W7nBnl_Z3I-4a5gLBiXvN6klPdvY&d=VdyLyaYSosf806FHw4nY1FzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=5415d190\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190108%2F59117924%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1O8vKbaOmP0Tz_96Cm6NjyU2LaJ46W7nBnl_Z3I-4a5gLBiXvN6klPdvY&h=f4b59eb6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190108/59117924?fbclid=IwAR1O8vKbaOmP0Tz_96Cm6NjyU2LaJ46W7nBnl_Z3I-4a5gLBiXvN6klPdvY</a>"},{"pid":"d765ac581c7e54f2a1f2435e2edaa52e571ccc63","tid":973619,"uid":103156,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T10:01:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qzncQu0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqzncQu0.jpg&h=c30f8bf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"597e76f33378b6f390ee6fca2dcc18b576d1a2b9","tid":973619,"uid":35790,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T10:01:35.000Z","msg":"取消香港政策法+1"},{"pid":"308726006c3724dd53b7f3d381427e64c022059a","tid":973619,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"